HEADWORD: enclosing
<hw>enclosing</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the act of surrounding something
with something else, so that it is inside the surrounding
object.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> inclosing, enclosure, envelopment, enveloping,
inclosure.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

